{"tid":1847741,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"越南宣告 其中一個北部主要關口 禁止中國旅客入境 峴港芽莊不接待中國人","createTime":"2020-01-28T07:39:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-28T07:59:00.000Z","uid":344304,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c3d6f3d255755516d377df5a76b7efc87dbf8074","tid":1847741,"uid":344304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T07:39:24.000Z","msg":"越南既老街市接壤中國河口市 僅一河之隔 交流頻繁<br />\n尋日已經宣布封關<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n英文source ：<br />\n<a href=\"https://m-english.vov.vn/society/northern-border-province-suspends-tourists-entry-exit-through-intl-border-gate-409331.vov\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm-english.vov.vn%2Fsociety%2Fnorthern-border-province-suspends-tourists-entry-exit-through-intl-border-gate-409331.vov&d=ib6ZiIlk8HgX3sh0XBbtb1KtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=c78c6245\" target=\"_blank\">https://m-english.vov.vn/society/northern-border-province-suspends-tourists-entry-exit-through-intl-border-gate-409331.vov</a><br />\n<br />\n越文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://tuoitre.vn/lao-cai-tam-ngung-xuat-nhap-canh-khach-du-lich-qua-cua-khau-quoc-te-20200127150937932.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftuoitre.vn%2Flao-cai-tam-ngung-xuat-nhap-canh-khach-du-lich-qua-cua-khau-quoc-te-20200127150937932.htm&d=ib6ZiIlk8HgX3sh0XBbtb1KtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=f2c711f4\" target=\"_blank\">https://tuoitre.vn/lao-cai-tam-ngung-xuat-nhap-canh-khach-du-lich-qua-cua-khau-quoc-te-20200127150937932.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同場加映一單新聞，一名支國7歲幼童係芽莊機場出境時檢出發燒，隨即移送隔離。但其支那父母不滿，因而大罵醫院，<span style=\"color: red;\">甚至威脅要拎刀隊冧醫生</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢篇得越文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.soha.vn/khach-trung-quoc-cam-dao-doa-chem-bac-si-tai-khanh-hoa-20200125162606817.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.soha.vn%2Fkhach-trung-quoc-cam-dao-doa-chem-bac-si-tai-khanh-hoa-20200125162606817.htm&d=ib6ZiIlk8HgX3sh0XBbtb1KtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=b4b6b43f\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.soha.vn/khach-trung-quoc-cam-dao-doa-chem-bac-si-tai-khanh-hoa-20200125162606817.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後越南旅遊勝地- 峴港同埋芽莊位處既慶和省 已經宣布停止接待中國旅客 唔租酒店比佢地 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其他地方都陸續採取類似措施<br />\n<br />\n都係越文source <br />\n<a href=\"https://nld.com.vn/thoi-su/khanh-hoa-ngung-don-khach-trung-quoc-vi-virus-corona-vu-han-nhieu-nguoi-se-that-nghiep-20200128095058793.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnld.com.vn%2Fthoi-su%2Fkhanh-hoa-ngung-don-khach-trung-quoc-vi-virus-corona-vu-han-nhieu-nguoi-se-that-nghiep-20200128095058793.htm&d=ib6ZiIlk8HgX3sh0XBbtb1KtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=60a8baf1\" target=\"_blank\">https://nld.com.vn/thoi-su/khanh-hoa-ngung-don-khach-trung-quoc-vi-virus-corona-vu-han-nhieu-nguoi-se-that-nghiep-20200128095058793.htm</a>"},{"pid":"af6b0eda507d699b8f24955e10070209b13ae4bd","tid":1847741,"uid":81140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T07:53:59.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"1038a70fa086c1f84e927bb8fc7f0b99e4e043a8","tid":1847741,"uid":50196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T07:59:00.000Z","msg":"呢啲先係國際標準"}]}